                                <head><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                                <p>The information given here as to the meeting and the participants
                                    is taken from the Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_295">p. 295</ref>. No record of the subjects
                                    discussed <pb facs="0416" n="316" xml:id="pg_316"/> at this
                                    meeting has been found. See, however, the editorial note on the
                                        <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName>–<persName corresp="#p_CC2">Churchill</persName> dinner meeting, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_307">p.
                                    307</ref>.</p>
